The epic situation?  As of now I'm one piece from the epic, the air crown... and honestly, as far as I've come, as close as I am to completing the epic, I would love to see the PoP pets stronger, since it would increase my power overall and be a help in general to the magician community.<br>
<br>
Don't really like the way PoP is shaping up for us magi, going to be a long road... one I might not feel like traveling.  Hear the cries of all the magi Verant, don't hold us down like this.  Peace out all.<br>
<br>
Eyce Freeborn, 57 magi of Lanys<br>
